txt.en: 'The Mead Hall is the central meeting place of the town, where all come together for feasts and parties in the good times, and where they gather and lock the doors to defend themselves in times of battle. There is much to add to bring life, warmth, and the history of Rohan to the interior of ours.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
